     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="8"/>
   <head>To the Author.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>IN representing to the whole Worldes view,</l>
      <l>The lyuelie Pourtrait of the Worldes Ad<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>mir'd:</l>
      <l>Yea, Natures Darling, with Her Pray<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ses due:</l>
      <l>With louelie Grace, and Merits Rayes attir'd:</l>
      <l>The Worth and Vertue of that Sacred Frame,</l>
      <l>Thy humble Service doeth thy Presse com<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>pell,</l>
      <l>To vindicate, and blaze abroade Her Fame.</l>
      <l>Each one must say, Thou hast deserved well.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>M. I. G.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
